This is the README file gives instructions on how to build the karabo framework.

The supported OS are: 
    SL5/6
    Ubuntu 10.04 LTS
    Ubuntu 11.10
    Mac OS
    Windows 7 (64 bit)

Other distributions like Fedora or Suse may still work.

(1) Dependencies

    If you have Ubuntu type:

        sudo apt-get install build-essential subversion cmake doxygen libnss3-dev libnspr4-dev libX11-dev python-dev zlib1g-dev python-qt4 python-qwt5-qt4


(2) Installation

    If you have root permissions on your computer, go to the directory of this README file and type:

    sudo install.sh



